column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,round(p.u,#),p.g,round(p.r,#),p.i,round(p.z,#), p.type,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.subClass, round(s.z,#) as spec_redshift,s.zErr as spec_redshift_Err,s.zWarning as Spec_redshift_Warning,  pz.z As Photo_Z, pz.zErr AS Photo_Err FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN Photoz as pz ON pz.objID=p.objid
